name: i n t e r s e c t i o n

metadata.name: Cosmic Earth
metadata.description:
An exploratory piece in morphology based on a simple square and circle. Partially generative and partially analogue. 

The connection between the noumenonological and ontological is a very important one as the science of real being gives us an insight into how we might create transcendentally in a digital atmosphere. Here lies the challenge of contemporary art as we are faced with exploring the relationship between the digital and the physical.

PrincePablos' genesis collection. 2023
3200 x 4000px
300dpi
